<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嗨，<tag a="110" b="4" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我們現在<delay20 />正在討論，<delay8 />
有哪些很棒的事情<delay20 />
可以和遠方朋友一起做喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay frames="24" />我想想<tag a="110" b="0" />
在相同的時間，<delay8 />
一起聽相同的廣播，怎麼樣？<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />即使住的地方很遙遠，<delay20 />
但還是能體會到一些<delay8 />共度相同
時光的感覺吧？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />總覺得有種<tag a="110" b="0" />
很浪漫的感覺呢～</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Aha" target="actor" targetSpec="" />然後，有一天！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我事先投稿的提問<delay20 />
就被拿出來介紹了<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊──我知道！<delay20 />　
是那種會連名字也一起被介紹的，對吧！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />順便問一下，你問了什麼問題呢？</message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><colour id="1" />請告訴我……向喜歡的人告白時，<delay8 />
能派上用場的的帥氣台詞。<delay frames="40" />
<colour id="65535" />之類的？</message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哇啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" /><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呃，咦？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這種問題，<delay20 />
跟朋友一起聽真的合適嗎？</message>
	<message label="015" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Aha" target="actor" targetSpec="" />然後，有一天！<delay frames="40" />
