就被拿出來介紹了<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="016" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊──我知道！<delay20 />　
是那種會連名字也一起被介紹的，對吧！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />順便問一下，你問了什麼問題呢？</message>
	<message label="017" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><colour id="1" />為什麼蝸牛的觸角<delay8 />
會有兩對呢？<delay frames="40" /><colour id="65535" />
之類的。</message>
	<message label="018" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哇啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" /><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呃，<delay20 />雖然有點在意，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但是那樣一來，<delay8 />
朋友到底該用什麼樣的心情去聽才好呀？</message>
	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" />也就是說，<delay20 />
不管是戀愛或者早餐，均衡都非常重要！</message>
	<message label="102" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果早上很忙的話，<delay20 />
早餐很容易就會隨便吃了呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過早餐並不是有吃就好，<delay20 />
均衡地攝取營養<delay20 />也很重要呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="103" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay frames="16" />呵呵呵，<delay20 />雖然今天早上也很忙，<delay8 />
但我可是吃了最理想的早餐喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="Surprised" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊，糟糕──！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />因為早上太匆忙，<delay20 />
結果我忘記穿褲子了～！<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="104" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這樣啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<colour id="4" />雖然你好像平常就沒有穿褲子<tag a="110" b="0" /><colour id="65535" /></message>
	<message label="201" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />藏幾個秘密在心中比較好<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
這麼一來，談戀愛時<delay20 />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />也會更加火熱呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="202" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但是<delay8 />我很不擅長隱瞞事情，<delay frames="30" />
所以這種事我實在<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />先不說這個了，<delay8 />你剛剛說的「<tag a="110" b="6" />」，<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是<tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />的口頭禪嗎？<delay frames="30" />
我覺得很棒喔。</message>
	<message label="203" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是嗎？<delay20 />
那麼，你要不要<delay8 />也和我用一樣的
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />口頭禪試試看呀？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="204" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />咦，<delay8 />可以嗎？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那我馬上來用用看！<pageBreak /><size value="150" /><anim id="Cheering" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Cheering" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是大笨蛋──！<delay20 /><tag a="110" b="6" />。<size value="100" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呵呵呵，<delay20 />這個口頭禪<tag a="110" b="0" />
果然非常棒呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="205" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嗯，<delay8 />還不錯吧？<delay frames="40" />
<colour id="4" />不過為什麼前面會是說那句話啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><colour id="65535" /></message>
